welcome boss bera.. you can do it on this sequence
bex > honey > bend > berps > bgt station

bex you can
- swap bera to other tokens
- used some of your swap tokens to add liquidity in pools and earn bgt

honey you can
- mint stgusdc to honey and vice versa

bend you can do and use your swapped tokens to
- deposit assets
-  provide or supply honey
- borrow and repay honey
- earn bgt by borrowing but its not working

berps 
- use honey to deposit on vault
- use honey to trade on berpetuals

bgt station to 
- use to bgt to delegate to validators
- voting in governance
- burn your bgt to gain bera (not recommended)
